claim.claim-text:
10. A suspension system comprising: 
a vehicle frame; 
a subframe secured to said frame including a pair of generally parallel subframe rails attached to said vehicle frame and a lateral support extending between said subframe rails; 
a pair of suspension arms pivotally attached to said subframe rails, and each independently pivotal at a first end about a pivot axis; 
an airbag mounted on an opposing second end of each of said pair of suspension arms and attached to said subframe rails; 
a spindle bolted on each of said suspension arm; and 
a shock absorber positioned between each of said suspension arms and said subframe rail.
